      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was going through my gran's old trunk and found this heavy silver signet ring. it has this crest on it—an owl perched on a broken sword, surrounded by stars. the metal feels... different, almost too heavy. i've been looking up these symbols and nothing matches any known noble houses. i feel like i've stumbled onto something that was intentionally hidden from us.",
